Text: Re Monmouth Meetingdo the play after dinner on PM To Mark mericancentury cc Subject Re Monmouth Meeting I had a note back from Doc asking if we wanted to go to the play after dinner If were not interested he can go on Sunday but if we want to go hell get us tickets I can go either way what do you think on AM To cc Subject Re Monmouth Meeting Then the Barnstormer it isa lot like the markets these days anyway on AM To Mark mericancentury cc Subject Re Monmouth Meeting Good meal in Monmouth Not sure if that is really possible by your standards I had the Barnstormer in mind It pretty much has to be better than the food at the Stockdale Center on AM To Mark Taylor cc Subject Re Monmouth Meeting OhYes I will be there I arrive early on Thursday in Moline Plan to visit the Boone grave site and then drive down I just signed up for the dinner thing yesterday Id rather be with you and Doc Maybe I can cancel once I get there I will send an email Are we going to get a good meal Mark Mark Taylor on PM To Mark mericancentury cc Subject Monmouth Meeting Are you planning to attend the planning committee meeting in Monmouth next week Im setting up dinner with Doc instead of the Private Dining Room affair in case youre interested
